The following is a list of commands that are processed by the CFS File Manager Application:

Global FM_CONCAT_CC
Concatenate Files

Global FM_COPY_CC
Copy File

Global FM_CREATE_DIR_CC
Create Directory

Global FM_DECOMPRESS_CC
Decompress File

Global FM_DELETE_ALL_CC
Delete All Files

Global FM_DELETE_CC
Delete File

Global FM_DELETE_DIR_CC
Remove Directory

Global FM_DELETE_INT_CC
Delete File (internal)

Global FM_GET_DIR_FILE_CC
Get Directory Listing to a File

Global FM_GET_DIR_PKT_CC
Get Directory Listing to a Packet

Global FM_GET_FILE_INFO_CC
Get File Information

Global FM_GET_FREE_SPACE_CC
Get Free Space

Global FM_GET_OPEN_FILES_CC
Get Open Files Listing

Global FM_MOVE_CC
Move File

Global FM_NOOP_CC
No Operation

Global FM_RENAME_CC
Rename File

Global FM_RESET_CC
Reset Counters

Global FM_SET_TABLE_STATE_CC
Set Free Space Table Entry State
